          <div class="eq-var"><div class="eq-var-name">Visibility</div><div class="eq-var-def">Space occupied in others' awareness</div></div>
          <div class="eq-var"><div class="eq-var-name">Contribution</div><div class="eq-var-def">What you actually produce for others</div></div>
